{"id":204711,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/01/维权网-安徽宿州女村主任遭乡政府关黑监狱治“/","date":"2012-01-03T10:55:32Z","modified":"2012-01-03T10:55:32Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽宿州女村主任遭乡政府关黑监狱治“精神病”（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\">      </a></span><span>（维权网信息员夏飞石报道）本网信息员日前得知：安徽省宿州市埇桥区北杨寨乡杨寨村民选女村主任王凤云，因为多次为村民维权向乡党委书记追问</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>万元土地补偿款，追查强行低价购买村民的土地。遭到乡政府联合多部门对王凤云进行打压，关黑监狱为她治“精神病”等折磨。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据悉，王凤云，女，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">57</span><span>岁，身份证号：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">342201195505189022</span><span>。汉族，初中文化，住安徽省宿州市埇桥区北杨寨乡杨寨村，杨寨村第六届村主任，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">208</span><span>票当选，当时有投票权的村民是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>人左右。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>事件起因是：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1996</span><span>年到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span>年桃园煤矿占用杨寨村里集体耕地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>余亩，已付补偿款</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>万元人民币，其中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>万元人民币被杨寨乡政府强“借”，至今九年不予归还。还有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">260</span><span>万人民币，被前村、乡两委干部挪用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>乡政府还强行低价“购买”村里</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">37.8</span><span>亩耕地，闲置至今，被丢荒；并将村委会的财务公章及村委会公章以“乡里保管”为由占为己有。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年，王凤云经村民选举当选为杨寨村第六届村主任。</span><span> </span><span>应村民的要求向杨寨乡乡党委书记赵存信追问</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>万元人民币土地补偿款下落，要求收回低价购买的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">37.8</span><span>亩耕地，收回村委会的财务公章及村委会公章，由此受到乡政府联合多部门的多方打压。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年元月，王凤云带领</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多名村民代表，向乡政府反映问题，乡政府党委书记赵存信却联合公安局、派出所，以</span><span> </span><span>“煽动群众扰乱办公秩序”将王凤云拘禁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，罚款</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span>元。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年，王凤云在北京日月星辰花卉公司打工。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>乡政府党委书记赵存信带领一帮人找到王凤云上班的岗位，将她绑架，蒙面关进一所不知名的黑屋里整整三天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，将王凤云押回安徽宿州市关进刑事二看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，刑事二看守所人员给王凤云戴一特大号脚镣，在宿州市主要街道沿街游行。之后将王凤云强行送到县医院“治疗精神病”，经医院检查王凤云根本没有精神病。又押回看守所关了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">37</span><span>天，这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">37</span><span>天中王凤云受尽了折磨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>浑身是伤。赵存信及看守所人员怕王凤云死在里面，才释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点，王凤云又到北京上访，在北京站突然被杨寨乡派出所原指导员彭敏和区公安干警王新平二人抓住，不由分说塞进警车，飞速拉到驻京办，交给区政府一王姓之人，并把王凤云所带的上访材料搜抢一空。在一个不知名的黑屋关押两日后，将王凤云强行带回宿州再次拘留了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日，本次共关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>截至到本网信息员发稿为止，王凤云还处在监视居住中，过着没有结束期限的监视居住生活。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-LhJyYXKGV-I/TwBicG36y5I/AAAAAAAAEI4/LtQYLgm0UjQ/s1600/SAM_0052.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-LhJyYXKGV-I/TwBicG36y5I/AAAAAAAAEI4/LtQYLgm0UjQ/s320/SAM_0052.JPG\" width=\"215\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-TD32oIpJr0g/TwBifpNXxNI/AAAAAAAAEJA/bN018Ll8YTw/s1600/SAM_0053.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-TD32oIpJr0g/TwBifpNXxNI/AAAAAAAAEJA/bN018Ll8YTw/s320/SAM_0053.JPG\" width=\"208\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-NF-maxRb7OU/TwBiihacP-I/AAAAAAAAEJI/0wlL7fDJCT8/s1600/SAM_0054.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-NF-maxRb7OU/TwBiihacP-I/AAAAAAAAEJI/0wlL7fDJCT8/s320/SAM_0054.JPG\" width=\"222\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WCxEWSUN1ew/TwBimLc9-9I/AAAAAAAAEJQ/w3Wog9Kykm0/s1600/SAM_0055.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WCxEWSUN1ew/TwBimLc9-9I/AAAAAAAAEJQ/w3Wog9Kykm0/s320/SAM_0055.JPG\" width=\"219\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-HQ3UIUc-3uw/TwBipDizIbI/AAAAAAAAEJY/XXpnzwqBGV0/s1600/SAM_0057.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-HQ3UIUc-3uw/TwBipDizIbI/AAAAAAAAEJY/XXpnzwqBGV0/s320/SAM_0057.JPG\" width=\"214\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1395737850564157782?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"450\" height=\"309\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n","author":1001,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9265,9555,8906,14602]}